Although they don't offer much in discounts, this place has knowledgeable and eager employees and owner to help with any questions, help you load things in the car etc and do seem to carry a wide assortment of grills and accessories along with books etc.
I really like the Barbeques Galore charcoal that they offer.
It is a big bag.
Lasted us a long time and is slow burning.
Will be frequenting this place often.

They are very nice to you right up to the point you make a purchase.
If you have any issues with the purchase, good luck.

